                                <p class="mb-4 size-18">A bachelor’s degree in Communications Studies prepares Marshall graduates for the widest range of positions across the professional landscape—career opportunities in state and federal agencies, nonprofit organizations, corporations, healthcare entities, and more. Marshall students who are interested in seeking advanced graduate studies will be well-prepared to move on to Marshall’s MA in Communication Studies program or other disciplines.</p>
                        <h4 class="header-colorize">Why Study Communication Studies at Marshall?</h4>
